de.polygonal.ds.Comparable

type
interface
Specifies that the order of an element in a collection can be determined by calling instance.compare(otherInstance).

Instance Methods

compare(other : T) : Int

Compares this object to other. The function should return 1 if this instance is 'bigger' than other, -1 if this instance is 'smaller' than other and 0 if both are 'equal'.
